{"tid":1706984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西灣河開槍後 美CECC主席施壓參議院本周表決《香港人權與民主法案》","createTime":"2019-11-11T08:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:36:37.000Z","uid":54373,"like":137,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b19ca380d40e0f8fd30a4737cb6fd5b9bf8d457b","tid":1706984,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:08:19.000Z","msg":"美國CECC主席麥戈文（Jim McGovern）在Twitter發文，宣稱香港警察「已經失控」，向參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）施壓，要求本周內在參議院表決兩黨都同意的《香港人權及民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港多地發生激烈示威活動，有警方開槍應對，西灣河有蒙面示威者中槍倒地，事態牽動中美人權議題角力。美國國會及行政當局中國委員會（Congressional-Executive Commission on China，簡稱CECC）主席、民主黨眾議員麥戈文（Jim McGovern）在Twitter發文，宣稱香港警察「已經失控」，向參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）施壓，要求本周內在參議院表決兩黨都同意的《香港人權及民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n中方暫未回應美國政界就今天香港局勢的表態。<br />\n<br />\n麥戈文獲知今日香港示威的消息後，先是在上Twitter稱，香港警察針對未持有武器民眾施加的暴力升級，此行為失控。他也tag美國總統特朗普的推特帳號，強調反修例狀況惡化，特朗普不應在此時保持緘默。"},{"pid":"2cb3e70aaf8589b8aae76e5f1c574bf2d20b6a8b","tid":1706984,"uid":89263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:09:37.000Z","msg":"美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fe3d3bd7eb410ed5a0594e40fed5e49bc52368","tid":1706984,"uid":143010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4786ab44afd849aae75857e589b9fec0d45f033","tid":1706984,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1620a71ce0ed38dacc6ebc30ace9912c562e2f56","tid":1706984,"uid":2429,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"收晒錢啦！條老野都等退休，老婆又係支那人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edfc3dd3a94418633